data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. ***SELLER IS OFFERING ROOF CREDIT WITH FULL PRICE OFFER*** You'll definitely want to come see this trendy 3/2 that includes a 2-car garage and additional flex-room. Use the flex-room as a 4th bedroom or quiet work-from-home office. Whatever your needs, this home certainly does not disappoint. There is a separate dining area and an eat-in kitchen with pantry. A spacious living area that is open to the kitchen makes for excellent entertaining. The hall bath has been remodeled with beautiful tile in the walk-in shower, updated flooring, vanity and fixtures. Each of the additional bedrooms is large enough for oversized bedding and have sufficient closet space. Indoor laundry area is stylish and makes for a welcome space to do a tedious task. The primary ensuite is a wonderful retreat within your own home. Welcome to luxury! The room has ample space for the largest of beds, while the 2 closets allow for separate and sizable storage. The primary bath has updated dual vanity, walk-in shower AND a large garden tub with a relaxing, renovated, atmosphere. The home is at the back of a quiet, small HOA community with sidewalks. Because the home is situated on a curve, the lot has a pie shape, giving a sizable rear yard. The fencing is on 2 sides and could easily be finished to provide security and privacy for enjoying the rear patio, fire pit area and new metal shed that will remain with the home. The owner is including the washer and dryer, it is minutes from downtown DeLand where Friday night has shops, venders, music and food. There is plenty of shopping only 15 minutes away; grocery, restaurants, retail shopping and entertainment. Only 45 minutes from Orlando Theme Parks and 45 minutes to the "World's Most Famous Beach - Daytona Beach".
